&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 2 Access to Work Admin Assistant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a positive, professional and confident individual to join our busy administration team, to provide administrative support for a member of staff who has a sight disability (&lt;strong&gt;25 hours per week on a renewable annual contract&lt;/strong&gt;) and to provide administrative support to our busy team here at Shropshire IAPT working from our office at Severn Fields Health Village, Sundorne Road, Sundorne, Shrewsbury, Shropshire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to possess excellent administrative skills, be capable of working under pressure and have the ability to keep a cool head in the face of a fast paced environment. In return we can promise you a very rewarding and enjoyable experience, working within a closely knit team delivering psychological therapies to services users across the county of Shropshire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to discuss this opportunity more, please contact us on 0300 123 6020 and ask for Kathryn Henegar quoting &#39;Access to Work Admin vacancy&#39;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;**We do not consider applications from recruitment agencies as part of Trust policy.**&lt;/p&gt;
